{"lemma":"حَبْوَة","slug":"حَبْوَة","root":"ح.ب.#","root_slug":"ح-ب-_","root_link":"/words/roots/ح-ب-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n7012","n7013","n7014"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%92%D9%88%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n7012","headword_ar":"حَبْوَةٌ","root":"Hbw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibaA='N","text_ar":"حِبَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]},{"entry_id":"n7013","headword_ar":"حُبْوَةٌ","root":"Hbw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"a subst. from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotabaY","text_ar":"اِحْتَبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Yaakoob, S, K,) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibowapN","text_ar":"حِبْوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, Msb, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HiboyapN","text_ar":"حِبْيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibaA='u","text_ar":"حِبَا=ءُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubaA='N","text_ar":"حُبَا=ءٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Ks, K:) meaning [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"act denoted by"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotabaY","text_ar":"اِحْتَبَى"},{"kind":"text","text":"; i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotibaA='N","text_ar":"اِحْتِبَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and also]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a turban,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"some other thing with which a man performs what is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAiHotibaA='u","text_ar":"الاِحْتِبَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Har p. 179:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubFY","text_ar":"حُبًى"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Yaakoob, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibFY","text_ar":"حِبًى"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Yaakoob, S, TA.) [See an ex. from a trad. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"namirapN","text_ar":"نَمِرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see also a verse of El-Farezdak cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hal~a","text_ar":"حَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] Hence,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hal~a Hubowatahu","text_ar":"حَلَّ حُبْوَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eaqada Hubowatahu","text_ar":"عَقَدَ حُبْوَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"mean (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He rose,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stood up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He sat."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 179. The former phrase is also mentioned in the S.) And the saying,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHubaY HiyTaAnu AlEarabi","text_ar":"الحُبَى حِيطَانُ العَرَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The things used for the purpose of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotibaA='","text_ar":"اِحْتِبَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"are the walls of the Arabs:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see 8]. (TA.) And the saying, in a trad. of ElAhnaf (when he was asked in a time of war, “ When is forbearance? ”), ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Einodi AlHubaA='i","text_ar":"عِنْدِ الحُبَا=ءِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"On the occasion of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AiHotibaA='","text_ar":"اِحْتِبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; meaning that forbearance is to be approved in peace, not in war. (TA.)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHbwp","text_ar":"الحبوة"},{"kind":"text","text":"on Friday, when the Imám is reciting the khutbeh, is forbidden; because"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlAiHotibaA='","text_ar":"الاِحْتِبَا=ء"},{"kind":"text","text":"induces sleep, and exposes the purity of the worshipper to be annulled. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibaA='N","text_ar":"حِبَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","Ks"]},{"entry_id":"n7014","headword_ar":"حِبْوَةٌ","root":"Hbw","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HubowapN","text_ar":"حُبْوَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":       -A2-  and see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HibaA='N","text_ar":"حِبَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":[]}]}}